Bill for an Act to phase out petrol vehicles by 2035 and introduce electric cars. April 17, 2019 In "News" Senator representing Bayelsa East, Ben Murray-Bruce and his amiable wife, Evelyn Murray-Bruce   are currently in a celebratory mood. September 7, 2018 In "Showtime People" The senator representing Bayelsa west constituency, Sen. Ben Murray Bruce, has enumerated in a video clip the psycho-causes of Nigerian Civil war in 1967 and the rationale behind the continuous agitation and cry of Biafrans over marginalization and unfair treatment by the federal government after fifty years of war. June 15, 2017 In "News"